race.comment: UPSTART LOVER (12) was quickly back on track missing a nose at Ipswich. He's likely to push over and race handy and back in class will be tough to beat. STANDLEE (4) has a wide gate to contend with but there will be scratchings. Won a 58 three back at Ipswich over 1350m and he's placed here as favourite the two since at a mile. He can feature with average luck. CLEARLY GEORGE (6) is busting to win and when close this track/trip last time. Maps for the run of the race and he's also a winning chance. ED I AM (8) is also fast and will be more effective coming back to this distance. has been kept on the fresh side and draws handy.
